QuestData.Title: Fast Expansion
QuestData.Description: Greetings, Commander.$B$BI am here on behalf of architect Baros Alexston.$B$BWe have gathered enough resources for the next phase of expansion.$B$BHe wishes to speak to you at your earliest convenience.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Baros Alexston at your garrison in Shadowmoon Valley.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, welcome, commander! Just the person I wished to see.
